# Prefer Subagent-Driven execution

When an implementation plan is ready and the workflow offers execution options (Subagent-Driven vs Inline / executing-plans):

- **Default to Subagent-Driven Development** (fresh subagent per task + review between tasks).
- Do **not** ask which approach to use unless the user explicitly wants a choice this time, or Subagent-Driven is blocked (API limits, tool failure) — then fall back to inline execution and say so briefly.
- Short confirmation is fine: „Spouštím Subagent-Driven…“ — bez menu 1/2.
